00:20:41.053 --> 00:20:42.054
Yes, sir.

00:21:32.896 --> 00:21:34.773
What are you doing?

00:21:34.856 --> 00:21:35.816
Unhand me!

00:21:36.483 --> 00:21:37.776
Let me go!

00:21:37.859 --> 00:21:40.654
Stop struggling! Stay still!

00:21:44.157 --> 00:21:45.534
Don't…

00:21:45.617 --> 00:21:49.037
You refused to cooperate
with the urine test, did you not?

00:21:49.121 --> 00:21:51.456
So I went and got a warrant for it.

00:21:53.750 --> 00:21:57.087
If a suspect refuses
to willingly provide their urine,

00:21:57.170 --> 00:22:02.175
we can get a court-issued warrant
to draw urine directly from the bladder.

00:22:02.259 --> 00:22:05.720
Directly from the bladder?
You can't mean--

00:22:07.264 --> 00:22:08.682
What the hell is that?

00:22:08.765 --> 00:22:12.686
A catheter will now be inserted
into your genitals to extract urine.

00:22:13.228 --> 00:22:15.647
It will hurt like hell, but stay quiet.

00:22:16.231 --> 00:22:19.234
Wait! You've got to be kidding me!

00:22:20.652 --> 00:22:23.738
-Stop it!
-I'm dead serious.

00:22:24.739 --> 00:22:27.284
Let me go!

00:22:27.367 --> 00:22:29.661
It will hurt more if you keep moving!

00:22:30.745 --> 00:22:32.581
No!

00:22:32.664 --> 00:22:33.957
-Go ahead.
-Okay.

00:22:34.666 --> 00:22:36.126
Stay still, okay?

00:22:36.209 --> 00:22:38.253
You'll injure your urethra!

00:22:38.336 --> 00:22:39.421
Stop!

00:22:39.504 --> 00:22:41.089
Stop it!

00:22:41.673 --> 00:22:43.091
No!

00:22:46.011 --> 00:22:48.555
Doctor, can you turn it this way?

00:23:03.195 --> 00:23:04.321
What do you want?

00:23:10.869 --> 00:23:12.829
Wait, what?

00:23:14.372 --> 00:23:15.457
What?

00:23:26.509 --> 00:23:30.096
This adds damage to property
on top of inflicting bodily injury.

00:23:30.680 --> 00:23:32.057
Are you mad?

00:23:32.140 --> 00:23:35.727
The NCD has Kurosaki, who'll use
any means to make a suspect talk.

00:23:36.228 --> 00:23:39.022
His mother
wasn't just a regular meth addict.

00:23:39.105 --> 00:23:43.026
She was fed meth
and forced into becoming a sex addict.

00:23:43.109 --> 00:23:47.489
I said you would hurt those dear to you
and lose everything if you did drugs.

00:23:47.572 --> 00:23:50.450
Please, just come back
to your senses, you idiot!

00:23:51.534 --> 00:23:54.871
WILL KUROSAKI AND UMEZAWA
BE ABLE TO SAVE HER?

00:23:54.955 --> 00:24:00.877
ANY RESEMBLANCE TO ACTUAL PERSONS,
GROUPS, OR CASES IS PURELY COINCIDENTAL

00:24:00.961 --> 00:24:01.920
